Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:46.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}許多人的思念 從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}致親愛的基爾伯特少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您還好嗎 別來無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您現在在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是否有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:28.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不論春夏秋冬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}四季輪轉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}惟獨有少佐的季節遲遲不來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我原本並不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一點也不懂少佐的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是在少佐所給予我的嶄新人生中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我稍微能感受到一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通過代寫書信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通過遇到的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:17.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐還在某處活著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一直 一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}即使不知道前途會有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也要一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:36.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果還能再次相見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:39.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:42.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我現在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}稍微明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:55.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「愛」的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:18.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 有代筆委託 非常緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:21.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}貝內迪克特 你去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:24.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為什麼啊 為什麼我要去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:32.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 客人在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我現在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:29.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.95,0:26:33.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客人有要求 不論身在何處 都能為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:35.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是自動手記人偶服務
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:42.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特·伊芙加登
